.SH NAME
.PP
pgglaskugel\-basebackup \- Creates a new basebackup from the database


.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\fBpgglaskugel basebackup\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Creates a new basebackup from the database with the given method.


.SH OPTIONS
.PP
\fB\-\-no\-standalone\fP[=false]
    Do not include WAL files in backup. If set all needed WAL files need to be available via the Archive! If set to false the archive is still needed for 'point in time recovery'!


